text.a: If this item is a group then the values here are a summary of the adjudication of the detail items. If this item is a simple product or service then this is the result of the adjudication of this itemadjudication
A sub-detail adjudication of a simple product or servicesubDetail
A claim detail. Either a simple (a product or service) or a 'group' of sub-details which are simple itemsdetail
A claim line. Either a simple (a product or service) or a 'group' of details which can also be a simple items or groups of sub-detailsitem
The third-tier service adjudications for payor added servicessubDetail
The second-tier service adjudications for payor added servicesdetail
The first-tier service adjudications for payor added product or service linesaddItem
The adjudication results which are presented at the header level rather than at the line-item or add-item levelsadjudication
Categorized monetary totals for the adjudicationtotal
Payment details for the adjudication of the claimpayment
